=Description=

"The Ecological Law and Governance Association (ELGA) seeks to provide a forum and a platform for diverse groups to work together and amplify their voices to transform our current human-centered, growth-focused legal paradigm, to an Earth-centered, ‘ecological law and governance’ paradigm to better protect the foundations of life.

Our vision is a just, flourishing world where state and global governance systems protect the foundations of life."

